From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: xq9mend <xq9mend@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 07 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] sshd_config: disable SSH agent forwarding by default

SSH agent forwarding is not required for SONiC operation. Disabling it
by default reduces the attack surface: a compromised switch cannot be
used to leverage the connecting user's SSH agent to access other systems.

Signed-off-by: xq9mend <xq9mend@users.noreply.github.com>
---
 sshd_config | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/sshd_config b/sshd_config
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/sshd_config
+++ b/sshd_config
@@ -87,7 +87,7 @@ UsePAM yes
 # and KbdInteractiveAuthentication to 'no'.
 UsePAM yes
 
-#AllowAgentForwarding yes
+AllowAgentForwarding no
 #AllowTcpForwarding yes
 #GatewayPorts no
 X11Forwarding yes
